      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is a fantastic diamond in the rough, ready for someone with a vision to bring it back to its former glory. While it's currently in poor condition and will require some dedicated mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a solid foundation for a rewarding restoration project. If you're looking for an affordable way to get your hands on a classic build, this is the perfect opportunity for you!",
